<div data-slate-editor="true" data-key="1498" autocorrect="off" spellcheck="false" data-gramm="false" style="outline: none; white-space: pre-wrap; overflow-wrap: break-word;"><div class="se-a5a14206" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1499"><div class="se-15a12e27" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1500"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1501"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1501:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">04、05 讲原计划下周一更新，为了响应催更要求，目前提前放出，期待你的评论与提问。如果觉得课程不错，也请分享给身边的朋友！</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-78f1e371  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1502"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1503"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1503:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">你好，我是黄佳。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-fb7a1956  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1504"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1505"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1505:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">通过前面三讲，我们已经完成了范式觉醒模块的两块地基。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-a7cc2237  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1506"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1507"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1507:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第 1 讲说清楚了为什么旧词汇不够用。GoF 假设结构性决策由人类工程师在设计期完成；Agent 系统把一部分决策搬到运行期、搬到模型手里，于是我们必须重新设计 Harness，让模型在不确定性里被约束地行动。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-8e9b2474  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1508"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1509"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1509:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第 2、3 讲建立了双轴坐标系。纵轴是认知功能，横轴是执行拓扑。一个模式必须同时回答 Agent 在做什么和数据怎么流。有了双轴，模式才有坐标、边界和失败模式。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-08933fc4  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1510"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1511"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1511:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">今天这一讲要补上第三块地基：怎么看懂</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1512"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1512:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-11c0a32f" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">真实工业系统</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1513"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1513:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-bc48ced2  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1514"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1515"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1515:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">比如我们打开一个 50 万行的 Agent 工程仓库，还是不知道从哪里下手，那些概念就停留在白板上。工程师真正要练出来的能力，是把一个陌生系统拆成可验证的结构图。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-339ea5ca  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1516"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1517"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1517:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这就是逆向五步法。其实也就是通过 5 个具体步骤来做逆向工程，剖析成熟的 Harness 框架。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-3fffb267" data-slate-type="block-quote" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1518"><div class="se-15a12e27" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1519"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1520"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1520:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Detect / Classify / Filter / Map / Verify</span></span></span></div><div class="se-15a12e27" data-slate-type="quote-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1521"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1522"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1522:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">找主循环，分组件，滤噪声，落矩阵，源码验证。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-93950614  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1523"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1524"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1524:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">你可以先浏览一下这张总图。后面还会详细解说。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-7e92e8d3" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1525"><img class="se-3d28c117" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/8d/2b/8d263d607eb2d96a6408da6c6146f32b.jpg?wh=5517x2671"><div class="se-2096ede2">逆向五步法</div></div><div class="se-2c92699e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1526"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1527"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1527:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">今天我会用 8 个 Agent Harness 当样本：Claude Code、Codex CLI、Aider、OpenCode、OpenClaw、Hermes Agent、DeerFlow、OpenHands。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-46312f36" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1528"><img class="se-ed9c6963" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/04/2c/04fe9663990b88a8cc3ba46922050e2c.jpg?wh=5162x3574"></div><div class="se-9be3f021  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1529"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1530"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1530:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">请注意，8 个框架只是素材。真正的主角是庖丁用来解牛的那把刀。我们是用这把刀来对市场上的各种 Harness 进行横切。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-5312c8c5  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1531"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1532"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1532:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">8 个框架会变，版本会变，目录结构也可能变。但只要 Agent 还需要感知、记忆、推理、行动、反思、协作和治理，逆向五步法就仍然适用。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-a8ad6298" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1533"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1534"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1534:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">为什么是这 8 个框架？</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-239749d1  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1535"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1536"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1536:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">当然你肯定会问佳哥：为什么偏偏选这 8 个框架？选样本不能全按热度榜来，也不能把 GitHub Trending 上的项目挨个讲一遍。我想为你呈现的是一张足够有代表性的工业横切面：从中既能看到 Agent Harness 的共同骨架，也能看到不同场景下的取舍。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-7529f732  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1537"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1538"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1538:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">一个好的横切面至少要覆盖三件事。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-84043e75  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1539"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1540"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1540:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一，要覆盖</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1541"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1541:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-7bba5816" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">不同主战场</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1542"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1542:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。代码 Agent、个人助手、多 Agent 编排、沙箱执行，面对的问题完全不同。代码 Agent 最怕看错仓库、改错文件；个人助手最怕身份、权限和长期记忆失控；多 Agent 最怕任务拆开以后收不回来；沙箱执行最怕“能做事“变成“乱做事”。如果只看其中一类，我们很容易把局部经验误当成通用规律。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-afd0844c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1543"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1544"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1544:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二，要覆盖</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1545"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1545:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-271a0f17" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">不同工程姿态</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1546"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1546:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。闭源产品、商业公司主导的开源项目、社区驱动项目，背后的约束不一样。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-c52bd835  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1547"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1548"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1548:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">大公司会把治理、权限、协议和可运维性做得更重；社区项目常常在一个关键不变量上打得很深。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-de3cad25  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1549"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1550"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1550:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">比如 Aider 的关键价值，已经超出“它能帮你改代码”这层功能描述。它抓住了 Git 这个核心不变量：所有修改都可以通过 diff、commit、rollback 被审计和控制。OpenCode 也类似，它抓住了 LSP 这个核心不变量，</span></span></span><a data-slate-type="link" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="1551" class="se-f828cddd se-8ab6c248"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1552"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1552:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Agent 可以借助 IDE 的语言理解能力</span></span></span></a><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1553"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1553:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，理解定义、引用、诊断和符号结构。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-4ef503f8  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1554"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1555"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1555:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">前者说明代码 Agent 必须进入版本控制系统，后者说明代码 Agent 必须进入开发环境本身。它们看起来是轻量社区项目，但各自在一个关键抽象上做得很深。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2dec341c  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1556"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1557"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1557:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三，要覆盖</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1558"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1558:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-15287aea" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">不同的“2026 变量”</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1559"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1559:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。2026 年的 Agent Harness 已经走过了工具调用演示阶段，开始呈现出更完整的系统工程形态。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-3321e0b9" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1560"><img class="se-e0ef8c7f" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/6c/6a/6caf057e5e385986f9a778e78c0acf6a.jpg?wh=3867x1981"></div><div class="se-70dfe025" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1561"><div class="se-cdf2bcd7 se-9a43091f" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1562"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1563"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1563:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一类是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1564"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1564:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-095e06b6" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">运行形态</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1565"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1565:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。Agent 不再只是一个网页聊天框，而是可以以本地可执行程序、CLI、IDE 插件、桌面应用、网页入口等多种形态出现。同一个 Agent 能力，正在被放进不同工作台里。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-9c22ed27 se-67385069" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1566"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1567"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1567:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二类是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1568"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1568:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-1b7b563d" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">协议与连接层</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1569"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1569:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。JSON-RPC、LSP、local-first gateway 这类机制，本质上是在解决 Agent 如何和工具、编辑器、本地环境、远程服务稳定通信的问题。没有协议层，Agent 就只能靠零散 API 拼接，很难变成可靠运行时。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-be98bfa9 se-8fb35f14" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1570"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1571"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1571:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三类是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1572"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1572:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-7b65c007" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">经验沉淀层</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1573"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1573:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。procedural skills 把一次次任务中的做法、步骤和失败经验沉淀成可复用流程。Agent 的记忆不再只是“记住事实”，还要“记住怎么做事”。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-58da9665 se-40043475" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1574"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1575"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1575:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第四类是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1576"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1576:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-6edfd49b" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">执行与隔离层</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1577"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1577:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。sandbox、权限控制、本地确认机制，解决的是 Agent 能行动以后如何不失控。只要 Agent 能改文件、跑命令、调系统，就必须有隔离环境和边界控制。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-3eb03f44 se-004f464d" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1578"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1579"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1579:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第五类是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1580"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1580:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-984228df" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">可观测与审计层</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1581"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1581:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。event replay、trace、日志、状态账本，让 Agent 的行动过程可以回放、调试、审计和复盘。没有这层，Agent 一旦做错，工程师很难知道它到底错在哪里。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-3d3650cb se-0a1d0336" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1582"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1583"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1583:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第六类是</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1584"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1584:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-ee364701" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">协作边界层</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1585"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1585:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。多 Agent 系统真正重要的，是每个子 Agent 的职责、权限、上下文范围和交接边界是否清楚。没有边界，多 Agent 就很容易变成角色扮演；有了边界，才可能成为工程系统。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-a59f4d75  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1586"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1587"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1587:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">也就是说，Agent 工程正在从“模型会不会调用工具”转向“模型如何被放进一个可靠运行时”。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2dd73126  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1588"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1589"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1589:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所以咱们可以把这 8 个框架当成八块标本，你可以参考后面这张表。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-d999ba6d" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1590"><img class="se-da877ba6" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/3d/d5/3db4cd8d0e8236e425bbbc7815c816d5.jpg?wh=4517x3490"></div><div class="se-2c80bdca  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1591"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1592"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1592:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">你会发现，这 8 个样本放在一起，刚好形成一个坐标系：左边是开发者工作流，右边是个人与组织工作流；整体上既包含感知和记忆，也有行动和治理，同时用协议、事件、沙箱、权限把模型的不确定性包起来。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-83f2d5b7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1593"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1594"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1594:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">我更愿意把它当成一次标本观察。产品很快过期，而标本背后的工程理念却能长存。我们真正要学的是它们为什么这样设计。</span></span></span></div><h2 class="se-5ea41ba4" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1595"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1596"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1596:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">为什么需要“逆向五步法”？</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-ce3ee7de  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1597"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1598"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1598:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">那么我们为什么还需要一把刀，也就是佳哥所谓的“逆向五步法”呢？因为我们读 Agent 框架源码或许会掉进一些坑。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-0f85ebcd  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1599"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1600"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1600:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第一个坑，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1601"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1601:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-1fde1c0a" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">README 幻觉</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1602"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1602:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。README 通常告诉你这个项目“能做什么”，但很少告诉你它“为什么这样做”。你读完以后，可能知道它支持工具调用、支持多 Agent、支持沙箱执行，但你仍然不知道：主循环在哪里？状态怎么传？上下文怎么装配？权限在哪里被卡住？换句话说，我们看到了功能清单，却没有看清系统骨架。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-85988b41  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1603"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1604"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1604:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第二个坑，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1605"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1605:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-8afce2c4" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">关键词漫游</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1606"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1606:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。很多人一上来就开始 grep：</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="1607" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1608"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1608:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">agent</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1609"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1609:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">、</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="1610" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1611"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1611:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">tool</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1612"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1612:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">、</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="1613" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1614"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1614:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">memory</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1615"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1615:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">、</span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="1616" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1617"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1617:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">context</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1618"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1618:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。结果跳出来几百个文件，每个文件看两眼，都像是重点。看了一圈以后，脑子里只剩下一堆碎片：这里有个工具注册，那里有个 memory class，那边还有个 planner。你以为自己在逆向架构，其实只是在源码景点观光打卡。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-88525192  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1619"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1620"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1620:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">第三个坑，</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1621"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1621:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-0af062b8" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">从入口函数一路钻到底</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1622"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1622:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。因为大型项目里，70% 的代码可能都是配置、日志、类型定义、序列化、适配器、UI glue、兼容层。你从 </span></span></span><span data-slate-type="code" data-slate-object="inline" data-key="1623" class="se-2fb309af"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1624"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1624:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">main()</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1625"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1625:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true"> 开始顺着调用栈往下钻，很容易钻进一条很漫长但不关键的支路。费了半天劲，文件看了很多，却忘了自己最初到底想找什么。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2d523c61  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1626"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1627"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1627:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所以，真正卡住大家的是缺少一个</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1628"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1628:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-176899b9" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">预期框架</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1629"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1629:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">。逆向工程的第一原则是：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1630"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1630:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-00aecc5a" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">先知道一个 Agent Harness 理论上应该长什么样，再去源码里验证它实际什么样。</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1631"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1631:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">没有预期框架，源码阅读就是信马由缰；有了预期框架，源码阅读才能按图索骥。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-37e3266e  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1632"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1633"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1633:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">那么，一个 Agent Harness 理论上应该长什么样？其实它的骨架很稳定。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-f80f6fde" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1634"><div class="se-0e4b6dae" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1635"><div class="se-0bc08a9e se-9bee1aa5" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-f2e3b33b"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1636"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1636:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">它一定有一个</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1637"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1637:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-87a9c209" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">主循环</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1638"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1638:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，负责接收输入、装配上下文、调用模型、处理工具结果，并决定下一步怎么走。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-c746c62f" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1639"><div class="se-b8fd1a14 se-f6fa98b1" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-1991d0ce"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1640"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1640:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">它一定有</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1641"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1641:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-63ee822d" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">上下文管理</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1642"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1642:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，否则 token window 很快就会失控，模型也会不知道该记住什么、丢掉什么。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-b5691305" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1643"><div class="se-92d88e1a se-b7517ece" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-19c493cc"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1644"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1644:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">它一定有</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1645"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1645:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-8b641b12" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">工具注册和调度</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1646"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1646:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，否则模型的行动空间就没有边界，不知道哪些工具能用、怎么用、什么时候用。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-cf619295" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1647"><div class="se-58794b5e se-9c1b29fb" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-32ae967a"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1648"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1648:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">它一定有某种</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1649"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1649:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-3e24505c" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">状态或事件记录</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1650"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1650:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，否则长任务无法恢复，出了问题也没法调试、回放和审计。</span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-c855e335" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1651"><div class="se-fc223aaf se-942e8b32" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-2ba17398"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1652"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1652:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">它一定有</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1653"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1653:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-ca17db88" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">治理边界</span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1654"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1654:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">，哪怕很弱，也会以权限、沙箱、确认、日志、策略等形式出现。因为只要 Agent 能行动，就必须回答一个问题：它被允许做到哪一步？</span></span></span></div></div></div><div class="se-8ed40346  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1655"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1656"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1656:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所谓逆向五步法，就是把这五个预期变成一套可执行流程：先找主循环，看 Agent 如何一轮一轮推进；再找上下文管理，看它如何控制模型看到什么；再找工具系统，看行动空间如何被注册、约束和调度；再找状态与事件记录，看系统如何支持恢复、调试和审计；最后找治理边界，看权限、沙箱、确认和日志在哪里真正生效。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-52cceea7  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1657"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1658"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1658:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这样读源码，就等于带着一张架构地图去定位。问题也从“这个项目有多少功能”，变成：</span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1659"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1659:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-a373f18d" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">它把模型放进了一个怎样的运行时？</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-9f6f0315" data-slate-type="image" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1660"><img class="se-d1eaee16" src="https://static001.geekbang.org/resource/image/48/b5/48afbee1935590f530fb9e63292536b5.jpg?wh=4005x1503"></div><h2 class="se-5534eb4b" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1661"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1662"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1662:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">逆向工程五步法</span></span></span></h2><div class="se-ee989e5a  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1663"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1664"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1664:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">好，接下来我们正式进入实操。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-7d5f001f  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1665"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1666"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1666:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">前面我们已经搭好了“认知功能 × 执行拓扑”这张矩阵。但矩阵本身只是工具。真正关键的是：我们能不能拿它去拆解真实的 Agent 框架源码？</span></span></span></div><div class="se-2886388a  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1667"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1668"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1668:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">我把这个过程提炼成五步。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-4a4bc0fd" data-slate-type="list" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1669"><div class="se-5726083c" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1670"><div class="se-7b834668 se-8aacf6b7" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-1d0b1567"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1671"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1671:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-28cb2ea5" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">探测（Detect），先找主循环。</span></span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-e5fc386a" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1672"><div class="se-224239d0 se-7814775a" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-344d4336"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1673"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1673:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-40582f94" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">归类（Classify），把组件归到七脉。</span></span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-b028e1da" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1674"><div class="se-77c313ae se-b5adf66a" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-8257d314"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1675"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1675:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-160e7c41" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">降噪（Filter），主动丢掉 70% 噪声。</span></span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-debbbb1a" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1676"><div class="se-1a1d405a se-b9c50da1" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-a86948e6"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1677"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1677:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-471de13c" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">映射（Map），落到双轴矩阵。</span></span></span></span></div></div><div class="se-6758669d" data-slate-type="list-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1678"><div class="se-3f3959d3 se-e3d00722" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-61c1530a"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1679"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1679:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="se-cb58a049" data-slate-type="bold" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">验证（Verify），回到源码验证判断。</span></span></span></span></div></div></div><div class="se-31786c9d  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1680"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1681"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1681:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这五步做完，一个原本很复杂的 Agent 框架，就会从“一大堆文件”变成一张你能看懂、能比较、能讲清楚的结构图。</span></span></span></div><h3 class="se-30408a2a" data-slate-type="heading" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1682"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1683"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1683:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">Step 1 Detect：先找主循环</span></span></span></h3><div class="se-1e93c324  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1684"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1685"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1685:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">所有 Agent Harness 都有一个心脏。这个心脏通常藏在一段不断重复的运行循环里，未必是 README 里最显眼的概念，也未必是项目里最有名的类。</span></span></span></div><div class="se-db3db863  " data-slate-type="paragraph" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1686"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1687"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1687:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">这个循环大概长这样：</span></span></span></div><div class="se-0e8e6341" data-code-language="shell" data-slate-type="pre" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1688"><div class="se-f98c06e3 se-06367549"><span></span></div><div class="se-7ff0fdd2 se-cc691b3e"><span></span></div><div class="se-2bca346f"><div class="se-cc2dbdff se-ac5963ee" data-code-line-number="1"></div><div class="se-cc2dbdff se-ac5963ee" data-code-line-number="2"></div><div class="se-cc2dbdff se-ac5963ee" data-code-line-number="3"></div><div class="se-cc2dbdff se-ac5963ee" data-code-line-number="4"></div><div class="se-cc2dbdff se-ac5963ee" data-code-line-number="5"></div><div class="se-cc2dbdff se-ac5963ee" data-code-line-number="6"></div><div class="se-cc2dbdff se-ac5963ee" data-code-line-number="7"></div><div class="se-cc2dbdff se-ac5963ee" data-code-line-number="8"></div></div><div class="se-df417625"><div data-simplebar="init"><div class="simplebar-wrapper" style="margin: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer-wrapper"><div class="simplebar-height-auto-observer"></div></div><div class="simplebar-mask"><div class="simplebar-offset" style="right: 0px; bottom: 0px;"><div class="simplebar-content-wrapper" style="height: auto; overflow: hidden;"><div class="simplebar-content" style="padding: 0px;"><div data-origin="pm_code_preview"><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1689"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1690"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1690:0" data-first-offset="true"><span data-slate-string="true">用户输入</span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1691"><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1692"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1692:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">  -&gt; </span></span></span></span><span data-slate-object="text" data-key="1693"><span data-slate-leaf="true" data-offset-key="1693:0" data-first-offset="true"><span class="hljs-language-bash" data-slate-type="mark-class" data-slate-object="mark"><span data-slate-string="true">构造上下文</span></span></span></span></div><div class="se-070d1c5c se-f7ea06f1" data-slate-type="code-line" data-slate-object="block" data-key="1694"><span data-sl